## Step 5
To approximate $P(1/2 \leq \bar{X} \leq 2/3)$, we need to standardize $\bar{X}$ to a standard normal variable $Z$. The formula for standardizing is $Z = \frac{\bar{X} - \mu_{\bar{X}}}{\sigma_{\bar{X}}}$.

