## Step 6: Calculate the percentage of patients with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure
To find the percentage of patients with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure, we first note that 19% have low blood pressure. Since 3.9% have irregular heartbeat and low blood pressure, the percentage with regular heartbeat and low blood pressure = 19% - 3.9% = 15.1%.

